'''Cartesian coordinates''' ''or'' (''US'') '''cartesian coordinates''' ''plural''

#(''mathematics'') The [[coordinates]] of a point measured from an origin along a horizontal axis from left to right (the ''[[x-axis]]'') and along a vertical axis from bottom to top (the ''[[y-axis]]'').

